social_posts.post_text: First and last engaged Valentine’s Day ❤️😘

✅ 75 hard complete! 

I will be a married man in ONE WEEK! @alexadobbins 😍❤️

My best man and many of the guys from my bachelor party joined me on this journey, swipe through to see some of their results! 💪🏼

I do NOT recommend doing this leading up to your wedding… 😅 The hardest part by far was trying to find enough time every single day while life was getting busier as the challenge went on! There was always a way…no matter how annoying it was 🤣

Looking forward to applying what I’ve learned from this experience into my more substainable, long term routine for good health and longevity. 🙏🏼
And now to spend forever together, reliving this moment for the rest of our days ❤️
We felt the love surrounding us on our best day 🥰❤️

Last photos before we say goodbye to our honeymoon! 💘

Super sad to leave our beautiful paradise but extra excited to get home and start living our best married life ❤️‍🔥🥰 (also cuddle our pups 🐕🐶)
Crumble celebrated his 7th birthday yesterday!! Golden birthday for our golden boy 🐕❤️

Welcomed my wife to the 30s club today ❤️ 

Happy birthday I love you @alexabanksdeck 😘
Relive the best day of our lives with us ❤️

I’ll be speaking at the first ever east coast @VidCon later this month!

I’ll be sharing how we have efficiently optimized my production process to post videos across every social platform for maximum reach / earnings potential, as well as doing this for all of our creator partners @deckedmedia 🙂
